                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- Mission 3 -->
              <div
                class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 hover:scale-105 border-l-4 border-blue-600"
              >
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <div
                    class="bg-blue-600 text-white w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full"
                  >
                    <svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      class="w-5 h-5"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                      <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M3 10h4l3 10h8l3-10h4"
                      />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="ml-3 text-lg font-semibold text-blue-700">
                    Build a Fair Economy
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-base">
                  We’re creating a balanced platform where everyone—users and
                  workers—benefit from value, security, and trust.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- Mission 4 -->
              <div
                class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 hover:scale-105 border-l-4 border-blue-600"
              >
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <div
                    class="bg-blue-600 text-white w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full"
                  >
                    <svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      class="w-5 h-5"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                      <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"
                      />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="ml-3 text-lg font-semibold text-blue-700">
                    Create Lasting Impact
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-base">
                  We believe in building long-term, positive impact in people’s
                  lives through consistency, trust, and innovation.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- Mission 5 -->
              <div
                class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 hover:scale-105 border-l-4 border-blue-600"
              >
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <div
                    class="bg-blue-600 text-white w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full"
                  >
                    <svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      class="w-5 h-5"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                      <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M20 13V9a8 8 0 10-16 0v4"
                      />
                      <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M4 21h16"
                      />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="ml-3 text-lg font-semibold text-blue-700">
                    Promote Trust & Safety
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-base">
                  We work to build confidence in every transaction by ensuring
                  worker verification, fair policies, and safe connections.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- Mission 6 -->
              <div
                class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 hover:scale-105 border-l-4 border-blue-600"
              >
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <div
                    class="bg-blue-600 text-white w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full"
                  >
                    <svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      class="w-5 h-5"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                      <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M12 11c0 2-2 4-2 4s-2-2-2-4a2 2 0 014 0z"
                      />
                      <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M6 20h12"
                      />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="ml-3 text-lg font-semibold text-blue-700">
                    Bring Digital to Daily Life
                  </h4>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-base">
                  We bridge the gap between tech and real-world needs, making it
                  easy for people to get help with just a few taps.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>


        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 border-t-2 border-gray-300 pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4" id="join">
            Join us now and experience the difference
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
            Start using our services with ease and certainty.
          </p>
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <button
              onclick="showAuthModal('register')"
              class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
            >
              Join Now
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
    </main>

